"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"Web3.0 is apparently tempting for investors at all levels, given the vision that the concept manages to provide to the audience. Full ownership of the content created by the artist, seamless interconnectivity between websites. It projects the vision of connecting the dots into one connected picture that enables US, the people, to finally take genuine control of the things we interact every day.\\n\\nHowever, skepticism continues to arise and raise concerns over the user-friendly perspective. The estimate of having a billion people to integrate into this brand-new concept wouldn’t stand a chance without having an easily understood, seamless, fully functional interacting point is equally important. It needs to go beyond a wallet, but a kickoff point for people, amateur or experienced, to have an equal chance of accessing the emerging concept.\\n\\n**<Blocto>**\\n\\nMore than a wallet, Blocto is described by its dev team as “Steam in the crypto space”. Imagine an unbiased application that acts as a joint between web 3.0, the API interface that opens up the gate of Web 3.0 for us to explorer\\\\~\\n\\nWeb3.0 概念提供的願景顯然對各個級別的投資者都具有吸引力。藝術家擁有創作的內容，網站之間無縫互聯, 使人能夠真正控制我們每天互動的事物。\\n\\n然而, 如果沒有一個易於理解、無縫、功能齊全的交互點，讓 10 億人融入這個全新概念的估計是不可能的。它需要超越錢包，而是讓業餘或有經驗的人有平等機會接觸新興概念的起點。\\n\\n<Blocto>\\n\\nBlocto 不僅僅是一個錢包，它的開發團隊將其描述為“加密領域的 Steam”。想像一個無偏見的應用，它充當了 Web 3.0 之間的接頭，API 接口為我們打開了 Web 3.0 的大門供我們探索\\\\~\\n\\nWeb3.0 概念提供的愿景显然对各个级别的投资者都具有吸引力。艺术家拥有创作的内容，网站之间无缝互联, 使人最终能够真正控制我们每天互动的事物。\\n\\n然而，如果没有一个易于理解、无缝、功能齐全的交互点，让 10 亿人融入这个全新概念的估计是不可能的。它需要超越钱包，而是让业余或有经验的人有平等机会接触新兴概念的起点。\\n\\n<Blocto>\\n\\nBlocto 不仅仅是一个钱包，它的开发团队将其描述为“加密领域的 Steam”。想象一个无偏见的应用，它充当了 Web 3.0 之间的接头，API 接口为我们打开了 Web 3.0 的大门供我们探索\\\\~\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/kkO1X7ctjqUlXzSjEj7nO.jpeg?height=777&width=1400)\\n\\n\",\"timestamp\":1634032621,\"title\":\"The hidden gem that opens the door of Web3.0 for investors.\"},\"digest\":\"eRkn4Gr0PpkH4ga1QIeFdpF7yBmYituGksiDN-VERWA\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0xc08232B0d3D662c7446f92E367dF2Cd56aBd050D\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"FDToQq8Qir0mbBMz0C4sbblDQ6nugBN_MNu79JKLZr0\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"hMBINqFBhdsSOQ3i5xeYY2VbP6d27z0yYY-Ob_FlZDI\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"3bji3xR-W3dujpoVhkEbkcrGindFY37JHOa5yHdERhUF8BGs60KDkc8hHVSuRLcbDGdkfX8MfpzUA-JEtfUlYw\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0x1ab8faba3e2adf4f49181e2ac346191d4a0d8077e8e3a33a48caf8bfb82f6c5f4edc58eaffb682826ea911d5779e0e71fb43e09355d10d81340fee15524bd2ef1b\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"FDToQq8Qir0mbBMz0C4sbblDQ6nugBN_MNu79JKLZr0\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"hMBINqFBhdsSOQ3i5xeYY2VbP6d27z0yYY-Ob_FlZDI\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\"SHA-256\"}},\"nft\":{},\"version\":\"12-21-2020\",\"originalDigest\":\"eRkn4Gr0PpkH4ga1QIeFdpF7yBmYituGksiDN-VERWA\"}"